{"tid":1797751,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（全港市民心聲）好憎警察一入商場搞到鋪頭落閘買唔到野","createTime":"2019-12-25T16:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T16:27:59.000Z","uid":5191,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dd5a344da7803da83b3c801de1f8148f0e7c7789","tid":1797751,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:26:44.000Z","msg":"話說同屋企人係九龍灣商場食完飯行行下<br />\n無啦啦有班警察沖入黎<br />\n我心：屌，我口號都無嗌會唔會拉我架<br />\n老豆老母：快d走呀，佢地一入黎就唔再安全<br />\n<br />\n屌那星，聖誕節想行下街，都俾佢地搞到鋪頭落閘<br />\n又唔見示威者叫口號會有鋪頭落閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82023055aac38fed6204f87dac462e4aad55213c","tid":1797751,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8937caa30b9cea414209882bb2e9ff651e2e9ea","tid":1797751,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:27:59.000Z","msg":"推"}]}